{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"My journey to coming here today"},{"time":4000,"text":"started in 1974."},{"time":6000,"text":"That's me with the funny gloves."},{"time":9000,"text":"I was 17 and going on a peace walk."},{"time":12000,"text":"What I didn't know though, was most of those people, standing there"},{"time":15000,"text":"with me, were Moonies."},{"time":17000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":21000,"text":"And within a week"},{"time":23000,"text":"I had come to believe"},{"time":25000,"text":"that the second coming of Christ had occurred,"},{"time":28000,"text":"that it was Sun Myung Moon,"},{"time":30000,"text":"and that I had been specially chosen and prepared by God"},{"time":34000,"text":"to be his disciple."}]},{"cues":[{"time":36000,"text":"Now as cool as that sounds,"},{"time":38000,"text":"my family was not that thrilled with this."},{"time":40000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":42000,"text":"And they tried everything they could to get me out of there."},{"time":44000,"text":"There was an underground railroad of sorts"},{"time":46000,"text":"that was going on during those years. Maybe some of you remember it."},{"time":49000,"text":"They were called deprogrammers."},{"time":52000,"text":"And after about five long years"},{"time":58000,"text":"my family had me deprogrammed."},{"time":60000,"text":"And I then became a deprogrammer."},{"time":65000,"text":"I started going out on cases."},{"time":67000,"text":"And after about five years of doing this,"},{"time":71000,"text":"I was arrested for kidnapping."},{"time":75000,"text":"Most of the cases I went out on"},{"time":77000,"text":"were called involuntary."},{"time":79000,"text":"What happened was that the family"},{"time":81000,"text":"had to get their loved ones some safe place somehow."},{"time":84000,"text":"And so they took them to some safe place."},{"time":88000,"text":"And we would come in and talk to them, usually for about a week."},{"time":91000,"text":"And so after this happened,"},{"time":95000,"text":"I decided it was a good time to turn my back on this work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":99000,"text":"And about 20 years went by."},{"time":104000,"text":"There was a burning question though that would not leave me."},{"time":107000,"text":"And that was, \"How did this happen to me?\""},{"time":110000,"text":"And in fact, what did happen to my brain?"},{"time":113000,"text":"Because something did."},{"time":116000,"text":"And so I decided to write a book, a memoir,"},{"time":118000,"text":"about this decade of my life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":121000,"text":"And toward the end of writing that book"},{"time":123000,"text":"there was a documentary that came out."},{"time":125000,"text":"It was on Jonestown."},{"time":127000,"text":"And it had a chilling effect on me."},{"time":132000,"text":"These are the dead in Jonestown."},{"time":135000,"text":"About 900 people died that day,"},{"time":137000,"text":"most of them taking their own lives."},{"time":140000,"text":"Women gave poison to their babies,"},{"time":144000,"text":"and watched foam come from their mouths as they died."}]},{"cues":[{"time":149000,"text":"The top picture is a group of Moonies"},{"time":152000,"text":"that have been blessed by their messiah."},{"time":155000,"text":"Their mates were chosen for them."},{"time":158000,"text":"The bottom picture is Hitler youth."},{"time":162000,"text":"This is the leg of a suicide bomber."},{"time":166000,"text":"The thing I had to admit to myself,"},{"time":168000,"text":"with great repulsion,"},{"time":171000,"text":"was that I get it."},{"time":173000,"text":"I understand how this could happen."},{"time":176000,"text":"I understand how someone's brain,"},{"time":179000,"text":"how someone's mind can come to the place"},{"time":182000,"text":"where it makes sense --"},{"time":184000,"text":"in fact it would be wrong, when your brain is working like that --"},{"time":187000,"text":"not to try to save the world through genocide."}]},{"cues":[{"time":193000,"text":"And so what is this? How does this work?"},{"time":196000,"text":"And how I've come to view what happened to me"},{"time":200000,"text":"is a viral, memetic infection."},{"time":203000,"text":"For those of you who aren't familiar with memetics,"},{"time":205000,"text":"a meme has been defined as"},{"time":207000,"text":"an idea that replicates in the human brain"},{"time":209000,"text":"and moves from brain to brain like a virus,"},{"time":214000,"text":"much like a virus. The way a virus works is --"},{"time":217000,"text":"it can infect and do the most damage to someone"},{"time":222000,"text":"who has a compromised immune system."}]},{"cues":[{"time":226000,"text":"In 1974, I was young, I was naive,"},{"time":230000,"text":"and I was pretty lost in my world."},{"time":232000,"text":"I was really idealistic."},{"time":235000,"text":"These easy ideas to complex questions are very appealing"},{"time":239000,"text":"when you are emotionally vulnerable."},{"time":242000,"text":"What happens is that"},{"time":245000,"text":"circular logic takes over."},{"time":247000,"text":"\"Moon is one with God."},{"time":249000,"text":"God is going to fix all the problems in the world."},{"time":253000,"text":"All I have to do is humbly follow."},{"time":255000,"text":"Because God is going to stop war and hunger --"},{"time":257000,"text":"all these things I wanted to do --"},{"time":259000,"text":"all I have to do is humbly follow."},{"time":261000,"text":"Because after all, God is [working through] the messiah. He's going to fix all this.\""},{"time":264000,"text":"It becomes impenetrable."},{"time":267000,"text":"And the most dangerous part of this"},{"time":270000,"text":"is that is creates \"us\" and \"them,\""},{"time":273000,"text":"\"right\" and \"wrong,\""},{"time":275000,"text":"\"good\" and \"evil.\""},{"time":279000,"text":"And it makes anything possible,"},{"time":283000,"text":"makes anything rationalizable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":290000,"text":"And the thing is, though,"},{"time":292000,"text":"if you looked at my brain"},{"time":294000,"text":"during those years in the Moonies --"},{"time":296000,"text":"neuroscience is expanding exponentially,"},{"time":299000,"text":"as Ray Kurzweil said yesterday. Science is expanding."},{"time":301000,"text":"We're beginning to look inside the brain."},{"time":304000,"text":"And so if you looked at my brain, or any brain that's infected with"},{"time":306000,"text":"a viral memetic infection like this,"},{"time":309000,"text":"and compared it to anyone in this room,"},{"time":311000,"text":"or anyone who uses critical thinking on a regular basis,"},{"time":313000,"text":"I am convinced it would look very, very different."}]},{"cues":[{"time":318000,"text":"And that, strange as it may sound,"},{"time":321000,"text":"gives me hope."},{"time":323000,"text":"And the reason that gives me hope"},{"time":325000,"text":"is that the first thing is to admit"},{"time":328000,"text":"that we have a problem."},{"time":331000,"text":"But it's a human problem. It's a scientific problem, if you will."},{"time":334000,"text":"It happens in the human brain. There is no evil force out there to get us."},{"time":338000,"text":"And so this is something that, through research and education,"},{"time":342000,"text":"I believe that we can solve."},{"time":345000,"text":"And so the first step is to realize"},{"time":353000,"text":"that we can do this together,"},{"time":355000,"text":"and that there is no \"us\" and \"them.\""},{"time":358000,"text":"Thank you very much. (Applause)"}]}]}